THIS WILL ASSIGN THE REBOOT OPTION IN THE POWER MENU ITS OWN IMAGE. IT WILL ALSO ADD BACK THE SLIDER TAB UNLOCK SCREEN. IF YOU WANT TO KEEP THE ROTARY LOCKSCREEN JUST REPLACE THE LOCKSCREEN.JAVA FILE INCLUDED IN THIS PACKAGE WITH JT'S FROM HIS SOURCE.

NOTE: YOU WILL ALSO NEED TO MAKE EDITS TO THE PUBLIC.XML IN FRAMEWORK-RES.APK FOR THE REASSIGNED REBOOT OPTION. SEE MY REBOOTIMAGE_REASSIGN_VENDOR FOR THE EDITS. 
